## æ€è·¯
Iterate the array from left to right, then from right to left to find optimal solution
## å…³é”®ç‚¹
Initialized Array to Integer.MAX_VALUE since we will be using Math.min function;
When we first start iterating , assume the matching character will be on the other end.

## ä»£ç 

